  EPiSODE iNFO 
                                                        
                                                                        
  The comedy news quiz celebrates a historic landmark 10 years since    
  the first guest host took the hot seat following Angus Deayton's      
  departure in October 2002, a short term experiment that has endured   
  to this day. Homeland actor Damian Lewis is in the chair for a fifth  
  time, while Merton and partner-in-mirth Ian Hislop are joined by      
  Spinal Tap and Simpsons actor Harry Shearer and UKIP leader Nigel     
  Farage, hoping to wring as many laughs as they can from the week's    
  headlines.                                                            
                                                                        
  Enjoy!
